name: Daenerys Targaryen
description:
Is a fictional character in the series of epic fantasy novels A Song of Ice and Fire by American author George R. R. Martin, and the television adaptation Game of Thrones.
Is the daughter of King Aerys II Targaryen (also referred to as "The Mad King") , and is one of the last survivors of House Targaryen.
Some of her titles: "Queen of the Andals and the First Men", "Khaleesi of the Great Grass Sea", "Mother of Dragons".
